'''穆斯塔法·-{zh-cn:阿迪卜;zh-tw:阿迪布;}-·阿卜杜勒·瓦赫德<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Botschafter in Deutschland|url=https://www.diplomatisches-magazin.de/botschafter-innen/mustapha-adib-abdul-wahed/|accessdate=2020-08-31|work=diplomatisches-magazin.de|language=de|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831140511/https://www.diplomatisches-magazin.de/botschafter-innen/mustapha-adib-abdul-wahed/|archivedate=31 August 2020}}</ref>'''（{{lang-ar|مصطفى أديب عبد الواحد}}，{{bd|1972年|8月30日||}}）是[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]政治人物、律师、教育家、学者，拥有法学和政治学博士学位。

==生平==
曾在黎巴嫩和法国的大学任教以及担任黎巴嫩总理[[纳吉布·米卡提|纳吉布·米卡提]]顾问<ref>{{Cite web|title=港口爆炸案后政府重组 黎巴嫩任命新总理|url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/world/2020/08/31/764262.html|accessdate=|author=海外網|date=|format=|publisher=|language=}}</ref>。2013年至2020年間担任黎巴嫩驻德国大使<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lebanese Ambassador: Blast a humanitarian catastrophe {{!}} DW {{!}} 07.08.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/en/lebanese-ambassador-blast-a-humanitarian-catastrophe/av-54487881|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809135814/https://www.dw.com/en/lebanese-ambassador-blast-a-humanitarian-catastrophe/av-54487881|archivedate=9 August 2020}}</ref>。2020年8月31日，他被选为黎巴嫩总理，接替因[[貝魯特大爆炸|貝魯特大爆炸]]宣佈辭職的前總理[[哈桑·迪亞布|哈桑·迪亞布]]<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-30|title=Lebanese ambassador Adib poised to be designated PM|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-crisis-government-idUSKBN25Q0PL|accessdate=2020-08-31|archivedate=30 August 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830231410/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-crisis-government-idUSKBN25Q0PL}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mustapha Adib on course to be designated Lebanon PM|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/mustapha-adib-designated-lebanon-pm-200830164828327.html|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=Azhari|first=Timour|work=www.aljazeera.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831014102/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/mustapha-adib-designated-lebanon-pm-200830164828327.html|archivedate=31 August 2020}}</ref>。

==政治生涯==

===黎巴嫩总理(2020年)===
2020年8月31日，穆斯塔法被选为黎巴嫩总理，接替[[貝魯特大爆炸|貝魯特大爆炸]]宣佈辭職的前總理[[哈桑·迪亞布|哈桑·迪亞布]]。穆斯塔法上任后，法国总统[[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙|马克龙]]二度访问首都贝鲁特，并向穆斯塔法提出一项「草稿计划」，以推动黎巴嫩的宗派改革以及结束数十年的腐败和管理不善的需求达成共识<ref>{{Cite web|title=In full: France's draft proposal for new Lebanon government|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/09/full-france-draft-proposal-lebanon-government-200903101156402.html|accessdate=2020-09-03|work=www.aljazeera.com|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903124814/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/09/full-france-draft-proposal-lebanon-government-200903101156402.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。穆斯塔法保证黎巴嫩各派承诺在两周之内建立一个具有改革意识的政府。

9月26日，穆斯塔法试图提出的新内阁团队名单，遭到黎巴嫩两大政党艾玛尔（Amal）及真主党阻挠，在会晤黎巴嫩总统米歇尔·奥恩后宣布辭職。穆斯塔法在电视讲话中说：「我无法继续筹组政府的任务，敬请让我卸下重任。」他向黎巴嫩人民致歉，表示他「无力实现人民的愿望，组成改革团队拯救这个国家」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lebanon: Prime Minister-designate Mustapha Adib resigns {{!}} DW {{!}} 26.09.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/en/lebanon-prime-minister-designate-mustapha-adib-resigns/a-55062582|accessdate=2020-09-26|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928192738/https://www.dw.com/en/lebanon-prime-minister-designate-mustapha-adib-resigns/a-55062582/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lebanon's PM-designate steps down in blow to French initiative|url=https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/world/2020/09/26/lebanons-pm-designate-steps-down-in-blow-to-french-initiative/|accessdate=2020-09-26|date=2020-09-26|last=Reuters|work=Free Malaysia Today|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005114742/https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/world/2020/09/26/lebanons-pm-designate-steps-down-in-blow-to-french-initiative/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

法国总统马克龙对此指责黎巴嫩的政治人物只是追求自己的自私利益，而不是该国的利益。

